-black\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-black mb-2\">Special Instructions (Optional)</label><textarea placeholder=\"Any special requirements or instructions\" rows=\"3\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 bg-white text-black\"></textarea></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-black mb-2\">Booking Type *</label><div class=\"space-y-2\"><label class=\"flex items-center\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"mr-2\" name=\"bookingType\" checked=\"\" value=\"once_off\"/><span class=\"text-black\">Once-off Booking</span></label><label class=\"flex items-center\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"mr-2\" name=\"bookingType\" value=\"recurring\"/><span class=\"text-black\">Recurring Booking</span></label></div></div><div><label class=\"flex items-center\"><input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"mr-2\"/><span class=\"text-black font-medium\">Weekend Work Required</span></label><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1\">If checked, admin will be notified for weekend assignment</p></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-black mb-2\">Payment Method *</label><div class=\"space-y-2\"><label class=\"flex items-center\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"mr-2\" name=\"payment\" checked=\"\" value=\"cash\"/><span class=\"text-black\">Cash Payment</span></label><label class=\"flex items-center\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"mr-2\" name=\"payment\" value=\"eft\"/><span class=\"text-black\">EFT Payment</span></label></div></div><button type=\"submit\" class=\"w-full bg-blue-600 text-white py-3 px-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors\">Proceed to Booking</button></form><div class=\"mt-6 text-center\"><a class=\"text-blue-600 hover:underline text-sm\" href=\"/\">Back to Home</a></div></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0yb2wil16uz6h.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]